{"tid":517091,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[勢如破竹］時隔7年，李克勤將於2018年推出國語專輯，繼續衝！","createTime":"2018-01-02T03:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T03:52:44.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"21dae4867e73806a34543feca5c9b8019a0fecfb","tid":517091,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:39:23.000Z","msg":"藝人李克勤昨晚在清遠體育館舉行的「第四屆粵語歌曲排行榜頒獎典禮」橫掃三項大獎，包括憑《失魂記》奪得「最受歡迎歌曲」、《30克》得「至尊專輯」以及「樂壇至尊歌手大獎」，克勤在頒獎典禮上更演繹經典作品《月半小夜曲》及《紅日》。李克勤透露事隔7年，將於明年再次推出國語專輯；至於演唱會方面，已經向多位樂壇好友發出邀請，希望能像早前與譚校長、容祖兒等的演唱會那樣的合作，為樂迷帶來不一樣的新碰撞。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實送禮勤浪費左幾多樂壇資源？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dde1ca30a02b14475027d352e998890f3bcbf3","tid":517091,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cb9e0f88a27741f9a5707c3964535a899d1324","tid":517091,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/114506_ef3ecc22f4f9067e0d9a7f347d6530d8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F114506_ef3ecc22f4f9067e0d9a7f347d6530d8.jpeg&h=2e2d813b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e44052dd31bfadb04b7c496505c770351529100","tid":517091,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"首席hater"},{"pid":"472322c1d0a17ded4473374707173f28e2653ff4","tid":517091,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e44052dd31bfadb04b7c496505c770351529100","tid":517091,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"首席hater"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"我事其事非其非 <br />\nHa你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}